entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've infiltrated the mine and eliminated the Controller and Grand Foreman
entries.journal_entry_description: Find and eliminate the Controller and Grand Foreman
entries.task01_task_display_string_1: You have defeated the Mine Controller.
entries.task01_task_display_string_2: You have defeated the Grand Foreman.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Report to Grenz Zittoun that the Controler and Grand Foreman have been eliminated
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: The Grand Foreman is somewhere in the depths of the mine. Find him.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Rel Rogock has seen better days. Your job is to make sure he doesn't see another day.
entries.task05_start_message: You hear the grumbling of a crazed individual.
entries.task05_utterance_wave_1: I have been waiting 1 week, 3 days and 5 hours for you to bring me my coffee. I condemn you to death!
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: The Controller is somewhere in the depths of the mine. Find him.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Teemu Komo is not well. Give him a taste of your medicine.
entries.task07_start_message: You hear the grumbling of a crazed individual.
entries.task07_utterance_wave_1: Why are you standing around?! I kill you now!
